text:
Hi content peeps! So excited to be here, have heard great things! A little about me:
• I’m a B2B SaaS content strategist (and recovering college English instructor). I’ve been working in SaaS marketing since 2016, both in-house at tech education and blockchain companies and now on my own as a consultant. I enjoy the independence of freelance life, but I’ve been also considering some in-house roles as I’m looking to grow in terms of content management/leadership. 
• I’ve been focusing a lot lately on helping teams cultivate empathy (yep, even in B2B) and use audience insights to inform brand positioning and content strategy. 
• I live in Boulder, CO with my spouse and our 11-year-old who is obsessed with the ’80s. At any given moment my house is likely filled with the vocal stylings of Whitney Houston and/or Duran Duran. (At least school’s back in session now!)
Looking forward to learning from you all! :wave:
